  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1008">
<l>naccap paṭātavaṉ celva naṭuvūru</l>
<l>ṇaccu marampaḻut taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of him who is disliked (by all) is like the fruit-bearing of the etty tree in the midst of a town.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
